# Pharmacy Sales BI Project 

End-to-end Business Intelligence project using the **[Pharmacy OTC Sales Data (2022](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/atharvasoundankar/pharmacy-otc-sales-data-2022)** dataset from Kaggle.

Sales performance analytics solution: data model, transformations, SQL analysis, and interactive dashboard.

# Business Scenario

- Sales performance over time  
- Top-performing products and categories  
- Differences between countries/regions  
- Opportunities for growth and margin improvement  

As a BI Analyst, the goals of this project are to:

- Design a sales data model
- Clean and transform the Kaggle transactional data  
- Build a set of KPIs and dashboards for stakeholders  
- Provide data-driven insights and recommendations

# Dataset

-Source: Kaggle – [Pharmacy OTC Sales Data (2022)](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/atharvasoundankar/pharmacy-otc-sales-data-2022)  
-Description: Simulated transactional sales data for OTC medicine across several countries between Jan–Aug 2022  

Main original columns (may vary slightly):

- `Date`  
- `Country`  
- `Region`  
- `Product`  
- `Category`  
- `Quantity`  
- `Unit_Price`  
- `Total_Sales`  

The raw CSV file is stored in:

```text
data/raw/pharmacy_otc_sales_2022.csv
